TO MAKE 'EM PAY?

244
00:15:39,313 --> 00:15:40,481
YEAH!

245
00:15:40,523 --> 00:15:43,150
YOU ALL WANT
TO MAKE 'EM PAY?

246
00:15:43,192 --> 00:15:44,694
YEAH!

247
00:15:44,736 --> 00:15:46,279
MAKE 'EM PAY!

248
00:15:46,320 --> 00:15:48,322
YEAH!

249
00:15:55,580 --> 00:15:57,540
NO SIGN OF 4587.

250
00:16:09,761 --> 00:16:11,137
[GUARD HITS FLOOR]

251
00:16:18,728 --> 00:16:21,481
YOU MADE QUITE
THE MESS THERE, QUEEN.

252
00:16:22,941 --> 00:16:25,192
TAKING OUT PRISON GUARDS
DOESN'T SEEM

253
00:16:25,234 --> 00:16:27,987
A VERY GREEN ARROW
THING TO DO.

254
00:16:28,028 --> 00:16:29,948
I GUESS THIS PLACE
REALLY HAS CHANGED YOU.

255
00:16:29,989 --> 00:16:32,867
I DON'T HAVE TIME FOR THIS.
RICARDO DIAZ IS HERE!

256
00:16:32,909 --> 00:16:35,954
AND HE WILL NOT THINK TWICE
ABOUT KILLING US ALL.

257
00:16:35,995 --> 00:16:38,372
NO, HE WON'T THINK
TWICE ABOUT KILLING YOU.

258
00:16:38,414 --> 00:16:40,416
YOU SEE, I JUST MET HIM.

259
00:16:40,458 --> 00:16:41,709
HE SEEMS
A REASONABLE CHAP.

260
00:16:41,751 --> 00:16:43,670
OF COURSE YOU'RE WORKING
FOR DIAZ.

261
00:16:43,711 --> 00:16:45,713
NO. I DON'T WORK
FOR ANYBODY.

262
00:16:45,755 --> 00:16:47,548
YOU SEE,
ME AND SAMPSON,

263
00:16:47,590 --> 00:16:50,134
WE GOT OUR OWN
PLANS, AS PER USUAL,

264
00:16:50,176 --> 00:16:52,094
BUT I COULD
ALWAYS TAKE

265
00:16:52,136 --> 00:16:54,472
A LITTLE TIME OUT
FOR A BIT OF FUN.

266
00:17:01,604 --> 00:17:02,897
[BONE CRACKS]

267
00:17:02,939 --> 00:17:04,398
AAH!

268
00:17:07,568 --> 00:17:10,738
[PUNCHES ARE THROWN]

269
00:17:10,780 --> 00:17:12,448
[GROANING]

270
00:17:28,965 --> 00:17:31,634
UGH!

271
00:17:31,676 --> 00:17:33,177
AAH!

272
00:17:33,219 --> 00:17:36,347
BEEN WAITING TO DO THAT
FOR A LONG TIME NOW.

273
00:17:36,389 --> 00:17:37,974
[CLANG]

274
00:17:38,016 --> 00:17:40,059
BAD MOVE, TURNER.

275
00:17:48,442 --> 00:17:50,403
SAMPSON...

276
00:17:50,444 --> 00:17:51,821
THAT WAS YOUR
FEMORAL ARTERY.

277
00:17:51,863 --> 00:17:53,531
YOU'VE GOT
MAYBE 6 MINUTES

278
00:17:53,573 --> 00:17:55,241
BEFORE YOU
BLEED OUT.

279
00:18:00,120 --> 00:18:01,497
[YELLS]

280
00:18:01,539 --> 00:18:04,542
-HYAH! HYAH! HYAH...
-HYAH! HYAH! HYAH...

281
00:18:11,090 --> 00:18:12,842
YOU'RE NOT GOING
AFTER THEM?

282
00:18:12,884 --> 00:18:14,510
I'VE GOT BETTER
THINGS TO DO.

283
00:18:14,552 --> 00:18:15,887
THANKS FOR YOUR HELP.

284
00:18:15,929 --> 00:18:17,680
IT DOESN'T MEAN I LIKE YOU.

285
00:18:17,722 --> 00:18:19,057
TURNER...

286
00:18:20,850 --> 00:18:22,769
HOW DID YOU GET OUT
OF YOUR CELL?

287
00:18:22,810 --> 00:18:24,854
HOW DID YOU GET OUT
OF YOURS?

288
00:18:44,290 --> 00:18:46,084
[THUD, RATTLE]

289
00:18:49,879 --> 00:18:52,465
WHAT ARE YOU LOOKING FOR?

290
00:18:52,506 --> 00:18:55,468
RICARDO DIAZ BROKE
INTO THE PRISON.

291
00:18:55,509 --> 00:18:57,762
PEOPLE USUALLY BREAK OUT
OF PRISON.

292
00:19:00,807 --> 00:19:02,433
HE WANTS TO KILL ME,

293
00:19:02,475 --> 00:19:05,561
AND HE WILL KILL AS
MANY PEOPLE AS HE HAS TO

294
00:19:05,603 --> 00:19:07,480
IN ORDER FOR THAT
TO HAPPEN.

295
00:19:07,521 --> 00:19:09,398
I THOUGHT I HAD A LOT
OF ENEMIES.

296
00:19:09,440 --> 00:19:11,818
DON'T HAVE A SIGNAL.
COME ON.

297
00:19:11,859 --> 00:19:15,321
DIAZ: HELLO. ARE YOU HAVING
TECHNICAL DIFFICULTIES?

298
00:19:15,362 --> 00:19:17,197
IT'S A LITTLE, UH,

299
00:19:17,239 --> 00:19:20,118
LITTLE GOING AWAY PRESENT
FROM THE LONGBOW HUNTERS.

300
00:19:20,159 --> 00:19:23,496
THEY JAMMED THE SIGNAL,
SO NO CALLS IN AND OUT.

301
00:19:23,537 --> 00:19:25,706
YOU ARE SO PREDICTABLE,
YOU KNOW THAT?

302
00:19:25,748 --> 00:19:27,625
YOU'RE TRYING TO MAKE
A CALL FOR HELP?

303
00:19:27,667 --> 00:19:31,504
YOU'RE
TRYING TO SAVE THE DAY?

304
00:19:31,545 --> 00:19:33,547
OHH.

305
00:19:35,341 --> 00:19:38,177
I HAVE SOMEONE HERE THAT
WANTS TO SAY HELLO TO YOU.

306
00:19:39,846 --> 00:19:41,097
GO AHEAD.

307
00:19:41,139 --> 00:19:43,349
DON'T DO ANYTHING HE
TELLS YOU TO DO.

308
00:19:51,273 --> 00:19:53,567
TRY AGAIN.

309
00:19:55,945 --> 00:19:59,323
YOU HAVE FAILED THIS CITY,
OLIVER QUEEN.

310
00:19:59,365 --> 00:20:02,451
DIAZ, THAT'S ENOUGH.
LET HIM GO!

311
00:20:02,493 --> 00:20:05,663
YOU SPEAK
AND PEOPLE DO AS YOU SAY?

312
00:20:05,705 --> 00:20:07,957
THAT'S HOW IT GOES?

313
00:20:07,999 --> 00:20:10,459
DOESN'T MATTER IF YOU'RE
RIGHT OR WRONG?

314
00:20:14,672 --> 00:20:16,382
NOT THIS TIME.

315
00:20:19,343 --> 00:20:21,387
NOT ANYMORE.

316
00:20:23,139 --> 00:20:24,473
[GAGGING]

317
00:20:24,515 --> 00:20:26,392
[GAGGING STOPS]

318
00:20:27,643 --> 00:20:28,895
HOW'S THAT FEEL?

319
00:20:31,814 --> 00:20:35,943
HOW'S IT FEEL, SOMEBODY
ELSE PLAYING GOD?

320
00:20:35,985 --> 00:20:38,154
THIS IS BETWEEN
YOU AND ME,

321
00:20:38,196 --> 00:20:41,365
AND NO ONE ELSE
NEEDS TO DIE, OK?

322
00:20:41,407 --> 00:20:43,951
DIAZ: WRONG!

323
00:20:43,993 --> 00:20:45,578
WRONG AGAIN.

324
00:20:45,619 --> 00:20:48,581
I WANT YOU TO SPEND
THE LAST HOURS

325
00:20:48,622 --> 00:20:52,585
OF YOUR PATHETIC LIFE
KNOWING

326
00:20:52,626 --> 00:20:55,504
THAT THESE MEN, THEY DIED...

327
00:20:55,546 --> 00:20:58,007
THEY DIED BECAUSE OF YOU.

328
00:20:58,049 --> 00:21:00,593
I'M COMING FOR YOU.

329
00:21:00,634 --> 00:21:03,387
BUT WILL YOU MAKE IT
IN TIME TO SAVE THE GUARDS?

330
00:21:03,429 --> 00:21:06,015
IT WAS HARD ENOUGH GETTING
THROUGH A FEW PRISONERS.

331
00:21:06,057 --> 00:21:07,975
I WONDER WHAT IT'S
GONNA BE LIKE

332
00:21:08,017 --> 00:21:12,105
GOING AGAINST
THE ENTIRE PRISON.

333
00:21:12,146 --> 00:21:14,023
[ALARM]

334
00:21:28,204 --> 00:21:29,705
KEEP YOUR HEAD DOWN.

335
00:21:29,747 --> 00:21:31,707
THEY'RE NOT GONNA MESS
WITH ME. THEY KNOW BETTER.

336
00:21:31,749 --> 00:21:33,417
IT'S NOT ABOUT THEM.

337
00:21:33,459 --> 00:21:34,752
DIAZ KNEW WE WERE
IN THE LOCKER ROOM,

338
00:21:34,794 --> 00:21:36,503
WHICH MEANS HE'S
WATCHING US.

339
00:21:36,545 --> 00:21:37,922
THERE ARE ONLY TWO ROOMS
WITH CAMERA ACCESS.

340
00:21:37,964 --> 00:21:39,423
THERE'S THE MAIN
SECURITY ROOM...

341
00:21:39,465 --> 00:21:41,341
NO WAY HE GOT IN THERE.
IT'S TOO FORTIFIED.

342
00:21:41,383 --> 00:21:43,343
THEN HE'S IN THE CONTROL
ROOM IN THE MESS HALL.

343
00:21:43,385 --> 00:21:45,263
THAT'S WHERE WE
HAVE TO GO.

344
00:21:45,304 --> 00:21:46,722
THERE'S NO "WE."

345
00:21:46,764 --> 00:21:48,015
I SAVED YOUR ASS

346
00:21:48,057 --> 00:21:49,558
SO YOU COULD GET ME
A DEAL WITH A.R.G.U.S.

347
00:21:49,600 --> 00:21:50,977
DOESN'T MEAN WE'RE
SOME KIND OF TEAM.

348
00:21:51,018 --> 00:21:53,104
DID YOU HEAR DIAZ?

349
00:21:53,146 --> 00:21:55,231
HE'S KILLING HOSTAGES.

350
00:21:56,816 --> 00:21:58,151
YOU SAID I WAS WRONG
ABOUT YOU?

351
00:21:58,192 --> 00:21:59,860
YOU SAID YOU'VE
CHANGED?

352
00:21:59,902 --> 00:22:01,361
PROVE IT.

353
00:22:04,991 --> 00:22:06,575
THE ONLY WAY TO
THE MESS HALL IS

354
00:22:06,617 --> 00:22:07,827
THROUGH THE CELL BLOCK.

355
00:22:07,868 --> 00:22:09,203
IT'LL BE 10 TIMES WORSE
IN THERE.

356
00:22:09,245 --> 00:22:10,370
THIS PLACE IS ALREADY
A POWDER KEG,

357
00:22:10,412 --> 00:22:12,039
AND IT'S ABOUT TO BLOW.

358
00:22:12,081 --> 00:22:14,292
IT'S THE ONLY WAY TO
THE MESS HALL.

359
00:22:16,210 --> 00:22:18,420
[ALARM]

360
00:22:21,799 --> 00:22:23,550
THESE INMATES ARE
GONNA KILL THEM.

361
00:22:32,518 --> 00:22:34,603
AND IF WE DON'T GET OUT OF
HERE, THEY MAY KILL US,

362
00:22:34,645 --> 00:22:36,605
AND, CLEARLY, WE'LL NEVER
MAKE IT TO THE MESS HALL.

363
00:22:36,647 --> 00:22:39,357
I'M NOT GONNA LET
INNOCENT PEOPLE DIE.

364
00:22:42,402 --> 00:22:43,654
[GROANING]

365
00:23:20,024 --> 00:23:21,234
[CLANG]

366
00:23:25,905 --> 00:23:27,405
UH!

367
00:23:27,447 --> 00:23:30,159
UH!

368
00:23:30,201 --> 00:23:32,036
HYAH!

369
00:23:32,078 --> 00:23:33,871
UH!

370
00:23:38,042 --> 00:23:39,001
NO!

371
00:23:55,184 --> 00:23:56,185
COME ON!

372
00:24:09,115 --> 00:24:11,700
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

373
00:24:11,742 --> 00:24:13,451
THANKS, QUEEN.

374
00:24:13,493 --> 00:24:15,246
WHERE ARE THE REST
OF THE GUARDS?

375
00:24:15,288 --> 00:24:17,081
A FEW OF THEM MADE IT
TO THE PANIC ROOM.

376
00:24:17,123 --> 00:24:19,541
SOME WERE TAKEN TO
THE MESS HALL.

377
00:24:19,583 --> 00:24:21,085
DIAZ SET THE INMATES LOOSE.

378
00:24:21,127 --> 00:24:23,837
HE CONVINCED THEM
TO GATHER UP THE GUARDS.

379
00:24:23,879 --> 00:24:28,092
LISTEN, A FEW OF MY BUDDIES
HAVE ALREADY DIED.

380
00:24:28,134 --> 00:24:32,305
IT'S LIKE DIAZ IS
KILLING THEM FOR SPORT.

381
00:24:32,346 --> 00:24:35,224
HOW MANY INMATES
IN THE MESS HALL?

382
00:24:35,266 --> 00:24:36,934
LAST I HEARD, AROUND 30.

383
00:24:36,976 --> 00:24:37,893
YOU GOOD TO WALK?

384
00:24:37,935 --> 00:24:39,186
YEAH, I'M GOOD.

385
00:24:39,228 --> 00:24:40,604
ALL RIGHT.

386
00:24:40,646 --> 00:24:41,855
TAKE THEM
TO THE PANIC ROOM,

387
00:24:41,897 --> 00:24:43,899
AND I'LL MEET YOU AT
THE COMMISSARY.

388
00:24:43,941 --> 00:24:45,401
NOT THE TIME FOR
A SNACK.

389
00:24:45,443 --> 00:24:47,027
IF WE'RE GONNA FIGHT OUR
WAY THROUGH 30 INMATES,

390
00:24:47,069 --> 00:24:48,779
WE'RE GONNA NEED WEAPONS.

391
00:25:08,757 --> 00:25:12,303
[SYRINGE DISCHARGES]

392
00:25:12,345 --> 00:25:14,472
I REALLY, REALLY NEED
TO TALK TO YOU.

393
00:25:17,350 --> 00:25:18,392
[THUD]

394
00:25:24,023 --> 00:25:26,524
OH, GOOD.
YOU'RE AWAKE.

395
00:25:26,566 --> 00:25:28,486
[EXHALES]

396
00:25:28,526 --> 00:25:30,237
I'M SORRY ABOUT
THE SEDATIVE.

397
00:25:30,279 --> 00:25:31,780
I WAS JUST TRYING
TO GET YOUR ATTENTION.

398
00:25:31,822 --> 00:25:34,658
IT'S OK. I...I UNDERSTAND,
STANLEY.

399
00:25:34,700 --> 00:25:35,659
I WAS JUST, UM...

400
00:25:35,701 --> 00:25:37,619
[CLEARS THROAT]

401
00:25:37,661 --> 00:25:40,538
BUSY TRYING TO STOP
DIAZ FROM KILLING
EVERYONE IN THE PRISON,

402
00:25:40,580 --> 00:25:42,333
YOU KNOW?

403
00:25:42,375 --> 00:25:46,462
SO, HONESTLY, STANLEY, I
THINK I COULD USE YOUR HELP.

404
00:25:46,504 --> 00:25:47,921
REALLY?

405
00:25:47,963 --> 00:25:49,131
YEAH. REALLY.

406
00:25:49,173 --> 00:25:50,383
[EXHALES]

407
00:25:50,424 --> 00:25:52,385
JUST, WHY DON'T YOU
UNTIE ME,

408
00:25:52,426 --> 00:25:57,223
AND WE'LL MAKE A PLAN
AND YOU CAN BE MY SIDEKICK?

409
00:25:57,264 --> 00:25:58,807
OHH! HEH.

410
00:25:58,849 --> 00:26:00,893
ACTUALLY, I ALREADY
HAVE A PLAN.

411
00:26:00,934 --> 00:26:02,144
[SNIFFLES]

412
00:26:02,186 --> 00:26:03,354
YOU KNOW HOW TO GET
OUT OF HERE

413
00:26:03,396 --> 00:26:04,604
THROUGH THE MORGUE,
RIGHT?

414
00:26:04,646 --> 00:26:06,982
SO WHY DON'T WE
ESCAPE THIS PLACE,

415
00:26:07,024 --> 00:26:08,566
YOU...YOU AND ME?

416
00:26:08,608 --> 00:26:12,112
YEAH, WE COULD,
BUT WHAT ABOUT DIAZ, RIGHT?

417
00:26:12,154 --> 00:26:13,780
WHO CARES ABOUT DIAZ?

418
00:26:13,822 --> 00:26:15,573
THESE PEOPLE DESERVE
WHATEVER HE'S GONNA
DO TO THEM.

419
00:26:15,615 --> 00:26:16,825
YOU KNOW THAT.

420
00:26:16,867 --> 00:26:18,118
YEAH. I...

421
00:26:18,160 --> 00:26:20,204
I CAN'T LEAVE ALL
THESE PEOPLE TO DIE.

422
00:26:29,422 --> 00:26:32,007
YOU WERE GONNA LEAVE ME.

423
00:26:35,219 --> 00:26:36,512
YOU WERE GONNA
ABANDON ME

424
00:26:36,554 --> 00:26:38,347
TO BRICK AND SAMPSON,

425
00:26:38,389 --> 00:26:40,266
AND I SHOULDN'T EVEN
BE IN HERE.

426
00:26:40,307 --> 00:26:42,893
I DID NOTHING WRONG.

427
00:26:42,935 --> 00:26:44,686
HEY, COME ON.

428
00:26:48,148 --> 00:26:49,691
IT WAS JUST BECAUSE

429
00:26:49,733 --> 00:26:53,320
YOU WERE GOING TO
ATTACK ME. OK?

430
00:26:53,362 --> 00:26:54,654
WHY WOULD I ATTACK YOU?

431
00:26:54,696 --> 00:26:56,949
BECAUSE YOU'RE
THE GREEN ARROW,

432
00:26:56,990 --> 00:26:58,451
AND YOU FIGHT BAD GUYS,

433
00:26:58,492 --> 00:27:00,202
AND YOU THINK
I'M A BAD GUY.

434
00:27:00,244 --> 00:27:01,495
AND YOU JUST THINK

435
00:27:01,537 --> 00:27:03,705
THAT I'M WHAT EVERYONE
SAYS THAT I AM.

436
00:27:03,747 --> 00:27:05,082
HOW COULD I?

437
00:27:05,124 --> 00:27:07,625
I DON'T...I DON'T KNOW
WHAT PEOPLE SAY.

438
00:27:07,667 --> 00:27:09,878
THAT I'M A KILLER,

439
00:27:09,920 --> 00:27:12,839
THAT
I'M A MONSTER,

440
00:27:12,881 --> 00:27:15,842
THAT EVERYTHING I DID,
EVERYTHING I DID...

441
00:27:15,884 --> 00:27:17,635
THAT WHOLE DUNBAR THING.

442
00:27:17,677 --> 00:27:19,721
IT WAS JUST LIKE
THE DUNBAR THING. I...

443
00:27:19,763 --> 00:27:23,850
I DIDN'T HAVE A CHOICE!
I DIDN'T HAVE A CHOICE!

444
00:27:23,892 --> 00:27:26,103
AND ALL THOSE PEOPLE
HAD IT COMING.

445
00:27:26,145 --> 00:27:28,730
YOU KILLED OTHER PEOPLE
BEFORE DUNBAR?

446
00:27:28,772 --> 00:27:31,733
HONESTLY, WHAT YOU AND I
DO IS NOT SO DIFFERENT,

447
00:27:31,775 --> 00:27:33,068
RIGHT?

448
00:27:33,110 --> 00:27:39,074
SO, LIKE, WE MAKE
SUCH A GREAT TEAM.

449
00:27:39,116 --> 00:27:40,826
SO WHY DON'T WE JUST
GET OUT OF HERE,

450
00:27:40,867 --> 00:27:42,244
MAYBE WE COULD WORK
TOGETHER AGAIN?

451
00:27:42,286 --> 00:27:44,704
OH!

452
00:27:46,206 --> 00:27:47,958
WHY'D YOU DO THAT?

453
00:27:48,000 --> 00:27:49,209
[ROPES SNAP]

454
00:28:02,889 --> 00:28:04,475
WHAT THE HELL
TOOK YOU SO LONG?

455
00:28:04,517 --> 00:28:06,684
IT'S A LONG STORY.

456
00:28:06,726 --> 00:28:08,521
HOW ARE FELTON AND MILLER?

457
00:28:08,562 --> 00:28:10,564
THEY'RE SAFE.

458
00:28:12,899 --> 00:28:13,775
TURNER:
I CAN'T BELIEVE

459
00:28:13,817 --> 00:28:15,319
I'M WORKING WITH
THE GREEN ARROW.

460
00:28:17,196 --> 00:28:18,197
YOU AREN'T.

461
00:28:19,573 --> 00:28:23,701
HEY, MAYBE...MAYBE PRISON
HAS CHANGED ME,

462
00:28:23,743 --> 00:28:25,621
COMPROMISED MY
JUDGMENT OF PEOPLE.

463
00:28:25,663 --> 00:28:27,373
YOU SURE THAT'S
A BAD THING?

464
00:28:27,414 --> 00:28:29,249
LOOK...

465
00:28:31,751 --> 00:28:32,961
NO OFFENSE.

466
00:28:33,003 --> 00:28:34,380
OK.

467
00:28:34,421 --> 00:28:37,633
BUT THE OLD GREEN ARROW,
HE WASN'T THE BEST.

468
00:28:37,675 --> 00:28:39,677
HE SAW THE WORLD
IN BLACK AND WHITE,

469
00:28:39,718 --> 00:28:41,345
BUT NOW YOU...
YOU KNOW

470
00:28:41,387 --> 00:28:43,180
THERE'S GRAY
OUT THERE, TOO.

471
00:28:44,890 --> 00:28:47,142
MAYBE THAT MAKES YOU
A BETTER HERO.

472
00:28:48,018 --> 00:28:49,019
YEAH.

473
00:28:52,398 --> 00:28:54,692
AND I KNOW IT'S
BAD FOR YOU,

474
00:28:54,733 --> 00:28:56,485
BUT DO YOU REALLY THINK
YOU'RE GONNA STOP DIAZ

475
00:28:56,527 --> 00:28:57,695
WITH A CAN OF SODA?

476
00:28:57,736 --> 00:29:00,322
WE'RE ABOUT TO FIND OUT.

477
00:29:02,782 --> 00:29:04,702
[GUARD SCREAMING]

478
00:29:05,911 --> 00:29:07,787
[INMATES SHOUTING INDISTINCTLY]

479
00:29:45,492 --> 00:29:47,661
ARE YOU PLANNING SOME
KIND OF LIGHT SHOW?

480
00:29:47,703 --> 00:29:49,663
SOMETHING LIKE THAT.

481
00:29:49,705 --> 00:29:51,415
IT'S NICE TO KNOW
SOMEONE HATES QUEEN

482
00:29:51,457 --> 00:29:54,460
AS MUCH AS I DO.

483
00:29:54,501 --> 00:29:57,671
IF IT WASN'T FOR HIM, I'D
STILL BE RUNNING STAR CITY.

484
00:29:57,713 --> 00:29:59,298
YEAH, ME, TOO.

485
00:29:59,339 --> 00:30:02,676
HE'S A COCKROACH.
HE REFUSES TO DIE.

486
00:30:03,761 --> 00:30:04,762
DIAZ!

487
00:30:14,104 --> 00:30:15,439
[BATON HITS RAILING]

488
00:30:15,481 --> 00:30:17,775
LOOK WHO DECIDED TO
COME TO MY PARTY.

489
00:30:17,816 --> 00:30:21,027
LET THOSE GUARDS GO.

490
00:30:23,781 --> 00:30:26,408
I TOLD YOU...

491
00:30:26,450 --> 00:30:31,747
THE ONLY THING I WANTED WAS
TO SEE YOU SUFFER...

492
00:30:33,666 --> 00:30:35,334
BEFORE YOU DIE.

493
00:30:35,375 --> 00:30:39,087
YOU'RE NOT GONNA GET
WHAT YOU WANT.

494
00:30:39,129 --> 00:30:40,172
NO?

495
00:30:41,965 --> 00:30:44,510
UH!

496
00:30:44,551 --> 00:30:45,761
[GROANING]

497
00:30:47,346 --> 00:30:51,183
OOH. I'VE BEEN
WAITING TO DO THAT

498
00:30:51,224 --> 00:30:53,644
FOR A LONG TIME.

499
00:30:56,146 --> 00:30:58,357
YOU GET YOUR SHOTS IN
WHILE YOU CAN

500
00:30:58,398 --> 00:31:00,734
BECAUSE I'M GONNA SEE TO IT

501
00:31:00,776 --> 00:31:03,320
THAT YOU SPEND
THE REST OF YOUR LIFE

502
00:31:03,362 --> 00:31:06,573
EATING YOUR MEALS
IN A SPOT JUST LIKE THIS.

503
00:31:06,615 --> 00:31:07,991
I PROMISED MYSELF

504
00:31:08,033 --> 00:31:09,743
I'M NEVER GONNA
DIE IN PRISON.

505
00:31:09,785 --> 00:31:12,412
AND I'M GONNA TAKE
YOU WITH ME.

506
00:31:12,454 --> 00:31:14,373
OH, YOU SURE ABOUT THAT?

507
00:31:19,419 --> 00:31:21,630
HYAH! HYAH! HYAH...

508
00:31:43,943 --> 00:31:45,404
TURNER: QUEEN!

509
00:31:48,198 --> 00:31:51,117
[TURNER GROANS, BRICK YELLS]

510
00:31:51,159 --> 00:31:53,787
[COUGHS, GROANS]

511
00:32:06,383 --> 00:32:07,384
QUEEN!

512
00:32:09,219 --> 00:32:12,556
CALLING FOR HELP WON'T SAVE YOU!

513
00:32:15,851 --> 00:32:17,436
THIS PLACE...

514
00:32:17,477 --> 00:32:19,813
IS GONNA BE ASH

515
00:32:19,855 --> 00:32:23,776
LONG BEFORE ANYONE GETS HERE.

516
00:32:29,656 --> 00:32:32,659
[COMPUTERS BEEPING]

517
00:32:47,758 --> 00:32:49,802
[BELL RINGING]

518
00:33:07,569 --> 00:33:08,862
OLIVER: COME ON.

519
00:33:08,904 --> 00:33:10,864
-GET UP! GET UP! COME ON!
-LET'S GO. GO! GO! GO! GO!

520
00:33:10,906 --> 00:33:12,532
GET GOING.

521
00:33:17,078 --> 00:33:17,913
WHAT THE HELL HAPPENED?

522
00:33:17,955 --> 00:33:19,205
DIAZ HAS
SOME SORT OF DEVICE.

523
00:33:19,247 --> 00:33:20,833
IT MUST HAVE TRIGGERED
AN ELECTRICAL FIRE.

524
00:33:20,874 --> 00:33:23,084
THE WHOLE PLACE IS
GONNA GO UP.

525
00:33:23,126 --> 00:33:25,044
YOU NEED TO GET THEM
TO THE SECURE COURTYARD.

526
00:33:25,086 --> 00:33:26,171
WHAT ABOUT YOU?

527
00:33:26,212 --> 00:33:27,506
I'M GOING AFTER DIAZ.

528
00:33:27,547 --> 00:33:31,217
YOU'LL NEED THESE.
NO HALF-MEASURES.

529
00:33:36,598 --> 00:33:38,057
[ALARM RINGING]

530
00:34:03,124 --> 00:34:04,167
[BLADE IS UNSHEATHED]

531
00:34:08,547 --> 00:34:09,756
JUST THE TWO OF US?

532
00:34:11,466 --> 00:34:14,678
[YELLS, GROANS]

533
00:34:18,264 --> 00:34:20,559
AAH! UH! UH!

534
00:34:29,275 --> 00:34:31,152
HYAH!

535
00:34:33,613 --> 00:34:35,365
[YELLS]

536
00:34:50,213 --> 00:34:51,631
[GROANS]

537
00:35:01,516 --> 00:35:04,519
I'M A LOT STRONGER NOW.

538
00:35:04,561 --> 00:35:05,812
[COUGHING]

539
00:35:13,653 --> 00:35:17,074
UH! OHH!

540
00:35:17,115 --> 00:35:20,660
UH! UH!

541
00:35:20,702 --> 00:35:23,622
PRISON'S MADE YOU WEAK.

542
00:35:41,098 --> 00:35:42,599
COME ON.

543
00:35:42,641 --> 00:35:44,893
COME ON.
GET UP.

544
00:35:44,935 --> 00:35:47,938
YEAH. YEAH.

545
00:36:04,830 --> 00:36:07,540
YOU'RE NOT
SURVIVING THIS.

546
00:36:15,090 --> 00:36:19,803
YOU JUST DON'T KNOW
WHEN TO QUIT, DO YOU?

547
00:36:19,845 --> 00:36:21,596
[COUGHING]

548
00:36:21,638 --> 00:36:23,098
I GUESS WHAT YOU
AND FELICITY HAVE

549
00:36:23,140 --> 00:36:24,390
IN COMMON, HUH?

550
00:36:24,432 --> 00:36:25,976
DON'T YOU SAY HER NAME.

551
00:36:26,018 --> 00:36:27,060
[COUGHS]

552
00:36:31,898 --> 00:36:35,027
FELICITY.

553
00:36:35,068 --> 00:36:39,656
DO YOU KNOW SHE TRIED
TO KILL ME?

554
00:36:39,698 --> 00:36:43,660
SHE PUT A GUN
RIGHT TO MY FACE.

555
00:36:43,702 --> 00:36:46,038
SHE WAS ABOUT TO PULL
THE TRIGGER.

556
00:36:46,079 --> 00:36:49,082
I DON'T BELIEVE YOU.
THAT'S NOT HER.

557
00:36:51,292 --> 00:36:53,086
IT IS NOW.

558
00:36:55,254 --> 00:36:56,798
THAT'S WHAT YOU MADE HER.

559
00:37:00,593 --> 00:37:02,554
[OLIVER YELLING]

560
00:37:19,946 --> 00:37:22,323
[GROANS]

561
00:38:20,423 --> 00:38:22,968
ARROW'S LITTLE SIDEKICK.

562
00:38:23,009 --> 00:38:26,179
HOW DID YOU FIND OUT
ABOUT THIS PLACE, DOVER?

563
00:38:28,014 --> 00:38:30,642
I COULD ASK YOU
THE SAME QUESTION.

564
00:38:30,683 --> 00:38:33,145
[CHUCKLING]

565
00:38:33,186 --> 00:38:35,855
WELL, THE ONLY WAY OUT
OF THIS PLACE IS

566
00:38:35,897 --> 00:38:37,398
THROUGH THE MORGUE.

567
00:38:37,440 --> 00:38:40,359
BUT YOU DON'T HAVE
TO BE DEAD.

568
00:38:43,905 --> 00:38:45,824
[BLADE STABS]

569
00:38:51,830 --> 00:38:53,165
[THUD]

570
00:38:53,206 --> 00:38:55,625
ACTUALLY,
I THINK YOU DO.

571
00:38:58,461 --> 00:39:00,839
YOU SHOULDN'T HAVE BEEN
SO MEAN TO ME.

572
00:39:13,852 --> 00:39:15,603
[INDISTINCT CHATTER]

573
00:39:30,702 --> 00:39:31,870
TURNER...

574
00:39:40,670 --> 00:39:42,380
THANKS.

575
00:39:42,421 --> 00:39:43,882
FOR WHAT?

576
00:39:43,923 --> 00:39:48,761
WITHOUT YOU, WE
WOULD ALL BE DEAD.

577
00:40:01,941 --> 00:40:03,818
[POLICE RADIO TRANSMISSIONS]

578
00:41:34,826 --> 00:41:35,994
MAN: GREG, MOVE YOUR HEAD!

